node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by H I G H T E A life on July 31, 2021 tagging @hightea.life, @puffherbals, and @upforhigher. May be an image of flower.

node.text: there are over 1500 smokeable herbs on earth, and while cannabis is certainly *our* leading fave, there’s one herb that herbal experts say should ALWAYS be present anytime we smoke. that herb: MULLEIN 🍃 the only herb that’s considered to help support the respiratory system as it’s being smoked, this cooling & moisture-driving herb helps offset the drying, heating properties of smoking. maintaining our lung health has never been a more timely topic & according to Lian herbal-queen of @puffherbals this magical plant is truly considered an ‘herb for smokers’ and a helpful addition to tobacco when trying to quit smoking cigarettes. at once a respiratory relaxant, moistening expectorant, cooling agent & nervous sedative. with hardly much taste! count our mullein in @hightea.life #highereducation via @puffherbalsmokes @puffherbals shot by @upforhigher
